      <p class="- topic/p ">The User Management feature enables you to create and manage the  <ph conref="../../../Warehouse/Product_Name_Warehouse.dita#reference-9043/product_name"
             class="- topic/ph "/> application's security roles, user accounts, and permissions.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">A security role is a task-based privilege providing the same level of access to modules and application data for a specific group of user accounts. Permissions are configured on a role, and users are assigned to the role to control how these users view or edit business data in the application.<fig class="- topic/fig ">
            <title class="- topic/title ">User Management Process</title>
