                   class="- topic/image "
                   placement="inline">
               <alt class="- topic/alt ">User Management Process </alt>
            </image>
         </fig>
      </p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">The User Management module enables you to manage the following:<ul class="- topic/ul ">
